Eveviwo, woakekeng wova tso Notse.  Nyitso didi, fia Agokoli no Notse.  Amewo kekeng, wono Notse le xome.  Amewo dibe woadzo, gake fia gbe.  Gbesiagbe, nyonuwo klo agbawo kple wonya awuwo.  Etsi ke kpoto, wo tsoe fugbe le xonti.  Ekpoto vide, xo gbang.  Eweviwo tso.  Woyi kpata kpata - Ghana, Togo, kple Benin.  Ameadewo yi Atakpame kple amebubuawo yi Lome kple Aneho.  Fifia, Eweviwo le sigbe 2.000.000 nene.
